Who I Am

About Me

"L'Oréal Brandstorm DACH Champion 2025 & Global Top 10 Finalist — out of 242,000 participants across 50 countries."

I am a strategy-oriented sales and business development professional currently completing my MSc Sales 4.0 at ESCP Business School (Germany · France · USA), with a GPA of 3.70/4.0. My background bridges rigorous engineering thinking — from a Bachelor's at BITS Pilani — with hands-on consulting experience across European media, logistics, and FMCG sectors.

My consulting work centres on commercial strategy, revenue model design, and go-to-market execution. I have co-created 40-page strategic playbooks, built cross-market sales dashboards for €2M pipelines, and led multicultural project teams across five ESCP campuses through my role as Head of Business Development at JET ESCP — the school's Junior Enterprise.

I am currently seeking a consulting or strategy role in Germany from May 2026, where I can contribute to high-impact client engagements with a structured, data-driven, and commercially focused approach.
